      "content": "Wait, are you sure? I was just looking at the raw data sheets from the lab earlier this morning, and the aggregate efficacy across the whole cohort looked pretty flat compared to the placebo. I didn't see any P-values under 0.05 for the primary endpoint in those files. Did I miss a specific analysis or a post-hoc adjustment that's driving that 0.001 figure you're mentioning?",
